'''''Polyhedron'' 100''' was a roleplaying magazine from [[October]] of [[1994]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including an adventure for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The article was called "[[The Tyaonon Ranger: A Fast Ship for Star Wars Campaigns]]" and was written by [[Bill Smith]]. Like all supplements printed in ''[[Polyhedron]]'' prior to [[2002]], the article is considered ambiguously [[canon]].

